        h3 Personal Loan Email Template 
        p The old Credible personal loan email template is pretty outdated. The visual style and layout is not consistent with other product's email template. I redesigned and developed Credible's personal email template to make sure it speaking to Credible's visual language and provide valuable information to users.
        br
