        img.full-width(src="/assets/internship/homepage-redesign@1x.png", style="max-width: 500px; display: block; margin: 1em auto; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,.5);")

        h3 Improve designer - engineer Collaboration Process
        p Last but not least, when I joined Credible, the design team used PhotoShop to deliver designs to engineers for inspection. But none of the designers are using PhotoShop as their primary design tool. We all have to convert sketch file to AI files and then save as PSD files. And sometimes PSD files could be very big and often crash. I introduced a spec tool - Zeplin to both design and engineer team and it improves the collaboration very well. Both design and engineer team are very happy to use it.

